LHS = \frac{1}{2} \left ( \frac {x}{2\sin \frac {x}{2} \cos \frac{x}{2}} + \frac{y}{2 \sin \frac{y}{2} \cos \frac{y}{2}} \right ) < \frac{1}{2} \left ( \frac{1}{\cos^{2} \frac{x}{2}} +\frac{1}{\cos^{2} \frac{y}{2}} \right )

